BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 1.650265 Tw (Artificial intelligence systems are increasingly deployed with the capacity to initiate financial transactions,) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.560015 Tw (manage healthcare records, execute legal instruments, and control physical infrastructure. These are not) Tj T* 0 Tw .393942 Tw (minor interactions. These are decisions with consequence. They affect money, health, rights, access, and in) Tj T* 0 Tw (some cases, physical safety.) Tj T* ET
Q
