BT 1 0 0 1 0 38.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 4.420307 Tw (validation, authority is inferred from system configuration rather than confirmed at execution, and) Tj T* 0 Tw .885227 Tw (responsibility becomes distributed across processes rather than anchored to a decision point. The result is) Tj T* 0 Tw (not random failure. It is consistent, repeatable behaviour operating under invalid assumptions.) Tj T* ET
