BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 2.056779 Tw (Authority cannot be transferred between individuals or systems. It is bound to a specific human, under) Tj T* 0 Tw .80726 Tw (specific conditions, at a specific moment. This is not a procedural restriction \227 it is a structural property of) Tj T* 0 Tw .079293 Tw (legitimate authority. Authority that can be transferred is authority that has been detached from its source, and) Tj T* 0 Tw (detachment from source is the point at which accountability breaks down.) Tj T* ET
